&gt;  At the Stanley recently I was surprised with the box use, and what 
was coming through for others. I just make the things, I don&#39;t know 
how it works, and it appears to work differently than what I 
expected. I also prefer the users speak of what it does. However, I 
expect a reaction from those that would keep this technology a secret 
to make attempts to show that it&#39;s only for a privliged few to use, 
and &quot;interpret&quot; for the masses. I&#39;m getting hints of this reaction, 
and have already shown my hand as to what side I&#39;m on. Right now it&#39;s 
the fear of evil spirits being released as an excuse as to why the 
common person should not use this stuff. That&#39;s same reasoning that 
keeps people away from other means of communication, like the quija 
board, channeling, dowsing, automatic writting......you name it.  No, 
you must pay a $300 an hour medium to communicate! Much money at 
stake for our insolence. 
